snippet.title: Heaven Forest - VR MMO Trailer
snippet.description:
The pressing human questions about life depend directly on our attitudes toward the universe. You'll find the answers you're searching for through a series of resonings and clues during your journey in this game as well as in your own life.

Available now on Steam for HTC Vive and Oculus Rift - http://store.steampowered.com/app/476480/
https://www.vrexplorer.net - a growing database of VR games, apps & experiences.
